summary: New male face texture, normal and specular maps.
descriptionHtml:
Retexture of male faces.
Texture & specular for all humanoids, normal maps for humans only.

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49766/?]FEMALE VERSION[/url]

[font="Impact"]Updates[/font]
[list]
[*]v.1.1. Oversharpeness & glossiness were slightly reduced.
[*]v.1.2. Wrong archivation was corrected, optional files with stubble/moles were added.
[/list]
[font="Impact"]Installation[/font]
[b]Manual:[/b]
Unpack the mod's archive and copy "Data" folder to your Skyrim main folder.
Replace everything it could ask to replace.

[b]NMM:[/b]
Just open the archive with NM Manager and activate by double-clicking on it.

[right][font="Impact"]Credits:[/font]
This texture is based on High Res Face Maps for Men, a lot of thanks to Geonox for the wonderful mod.[/right]
